[{'text': 'I will never say that I am great at fighting
games, in fact I wont even go as far as', 'start': 17.949, 'duration': 7.13}, {'text': 'to say that I am particularly good at any
fighting games.', 'start': 25.079, 'duration': 3.301}, {'text': 'But this does not take away from the fact
that I really like fighting game, specifically', 'start': 28.38, 'duration': 5.94}, {'text': 'the Street Fighter series.', 'start': 34.32, 'duration': 1.35}, {'text': 'I look forward to each entry, be it a remake,
an add on, a version that updates one particular', 'start': 35.67, 'duration': 5.69}, {'text': 'frame of animation, or the possibility of
a true next game.', 'start': 41.36, 'duration': 5.83}, {'text': 'I mean its been over twenty years and we are
only up to four, so Im not holding my breath', 'start': 47.19, 'duration': 5.59}, {'text': 'until five comes out.', 'start': 52.78, 'duration': 1.54}, {'text': 'The point is, I like Street Fighter.', 'start': 54.32, 'duration': 2.32}, {'text': 'So when Street Fighter 2 got the HD update
and released for the PSN, I ate that up.', 'start': 56.64, 'duration': 13.24}, {'text': 'After I had gotten my fill, I began to wonder
if Street Fighter 3 would ever get this treatment.', 'start': 69.88, 'duration': 5.0}, {'text': 'Well it took long enough but finally Street
Fighter 3: Online Edition was released.', 'start': 74.88, 'duration': 5.55}, {'text': 'Street Fighter 3: 3rd Strike is a very different
game than both Street Fighter 2 and 4.', 'start': 80.43, 'duration': 5.42}, {'text': 'While those two games play very similar to
one another, Street Fighter 3 is very unique', 'start': 85.85, 'duration': 4.86}, {'text': 'to itself.', 'start': 90.71, 'duration': 1.28}, {'text': 'Using a very different fighting mechanic,
Street Fighter 3 can be intimidating to new', 'start': 91.99, 'duration': 4.919}, {'text': 'players.', 'start': 96.909, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'The matches are very fast and require a lot
of skill, not that previous games didnt,', 'start': 97.909, 'duration': 6.21}, {'text': 'but this one has probably the highest learning
curve.', 'start': 104.119, 'duration': 3.38}, {'text': 'One major thing the game introduced was the
parry system.', 'start': 107.499, 'duration': 3.32}, {'text': 'By moving your character forward at the exact
moment, you can block an oncoming attack without', 'start': 110.819, 'duration': 7.031}, {'text': 'receiving any damage, also this opens up a
window for a counterattack.', 'start': 117.85, 'duration': 4.969}, {'text': 'Needless to say, this introduces a completely
new aspect to the fighting.', 'start': 122.819, 'duration': 4.98}, {'text': 'You have to time it perfectly, which requires
a lot of time and practice.', 'start': 127.799, 'duration': 6.171}, {'text': 'The game also mixed things up by having an
almost entirely new roster, which means hundreds', 'start': 133.97, 'duration': 5.16}, {'text': 'of new moves to learn.', 'start': 139.13, 'duration': 1.38}, {'text': 'There of course is Ryu, Ken, Akuma and Chun-Li,
but that is just about it.', 'start': 140.51, 'duration': 6.09}, {'text': 'Everyone else was completely new and this
was not the most accepted idea.The new main', 'start': 146.6, 'duration': 5.21}, {'text': 'character is Alex and many of the characters
are very unusual and play strangely but after', 'start': 151.81, 'duration': 6.45}, {'text': 'you play a little they will become as endeared
to you as previous characters.', 'start': 158.26, 'duration': 4.679}, {'text': 'My favorites are Dudley, an English old school
boxer and Oro, a hermit who binds his one', 'start': 162.939, 'duration': 5.401}, {'text': 'arm so he doesnt kill anyone which I just
think is pretty cool.', 'start': 168.34, 'duration': 6.84}, {'text': 'This HD release is the version fans have been
waiting for.', 'start': 175.18, 'duration': 8.5}, {'text': 'With so many new things added, this is not
simply just a port.', 'start': 183.68, 'duration': 4.16}, {'text': 'The game has many different screen modes,
from widescreen to one that looks like an', 'start': 187.84, 'duration': 4.42}, {'text': 'arcade cabinet.', 'start': 192.26, 'duration': 1.559}, {'text': 'I like to leave it in the 4:3 because along
the side it shows all the challenges you complete.', 'start': 193.819, 'duration': 5.78}, {'text': 'Doing these unlock points that can be used
to buy concept arts and other things.', 'start': 199.599, 'duration': 4.041}, {'text': 'It is a great addition that has you always
coming back.', 'start': 203.64, 'duration': 4.14}, {'text': 'There are also training stages added which
I recommend if you are new to this game.', 'start': 207.78, 'duration': 4.23}, {'text': 'It will teach you the finer parts of the fighting
but also offer things for experienced players.', 'start': 212.01, 'duration': 5.839}, {'text': 'And of course because this is called Online
Edition there is online mode where you can', 'start': 217.849, 'duration': 4.661}, {'text': 'test what you have learned.', 'start': 222.51, 'duration': 1.709}, {'text': 'The online runs smooth with little to no connection
problems or lag, and many different game modes', 'start': 224.219, 'duration': 5.66}, {'text': 'to fight in.', 'start': 229.879, 'duration': 1.491}, {'text': 'It makes for the perfect addition to an already
great game.', 'start': 231.37, 'duration': 11.42}, {'text': 'Street Fighter 3 has always had the stigma
of not being Street Fighter 2.', 'start': 242.79, 'duration': 4.15}, {'text': 'It is really different and some people did
not accept it because of this.', 'start': 246.94, 'duration': 5.43}, {'text': 'Personally I like the fact that it is different,
after re-release after re-release of Street', 'start': 252.37, 'duration': 5.28}, {'text': 'Fighter 2, it was nice for something so different.', 'start': 257.65, 'duration': 3.559}, {'text': 'With this release hopefully more people accept
it and allow it to take its place as one of', 'start': 261.209, 'duration': 5.041}, {'text': 'the best fighters.', 'start': 266.25, 'duration': 12.88}]
